sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as Apache Pulsar<br/>(message queue)
    participant B as backend12<br/>(batch processor)
    participant RL as Rate Limiter<br/>(multi-quota mapping)
    participant APIM as Apigee / APIM
    participant US as Underlying Service<br/>(Routing / Search API)
    participant BS as Azure Blob Storage

    P->>B: deliver batch message (batchId, apiKey, items[])
    activate B
    note over B: max 40 concurrent batches<br/>per service (Pulsar unacked limit)

    loop For each item in batch
        B->>RL: request slot (quota name = endpoint type)
        note over RL: multi-quota-mapping:<br/>routing1, search1, geocode1,<br/>reverse-geocode1, etc.
        RL-->>RL: check concurrent requests limit<br/>(derived from customer QPS × multiplier)
        alt slot available
            RL-->>B: grant slot
            B->>APIM: HTTP request (client API key, item payload)
            APIM-->>APIM: enforce per-second quota<br/>(OnlineRouting_quotaPerSecond etc.)
            APIM->>US: forward to underlying service
            US-->>APIM: response (200 / 4xx / 5xx)
            APIM-->>B: response
            B-->>RL: release slot
            B-->>B: store item result
        else quota exceeded (429 / 403)
            APIM-->>B: 429 Too Many Requests
            B-->>RL: release slot
            B-->>B: back-off & retry item
        end
    end

    B->>BS: write aggregated result file (batchId.json)
    BS-->>B: write confirmed
    B-->>P: ack message (remove from backlog)
    deactivate B
